    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as cherished. This car is absolutely stunning\u2014I\u2019ve kept it in pristine condition, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every curve is flawless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve babied this one from day one, so you\u2019re getting a real gem that\u2019s ready for the open road. Come by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this ride!",
