      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade specimen that redefines the apex-hunting experience. This unit features a precision-balanced rotating assembly and a bespoke stage-2 thermal management suite, ensuring the forced induction remains optimal under high-load cycles. The suspension geometry has been surgically recalibrated with adjustable coilovers and reinforced bushings for zero-deflection cornering. Every fluid flush has been documented with laboratory-grade synthetics, and the drivetrain engagement is crisp, thanks to a lightweight flywheel and a heavy-duty clutch assembly. The chassis rigidity is impeccable, free of any stress-cycling fatigue. This is a turn-key solution for the enthusiast who demands uncompromising mechanical integrity and a linear power delivery that pulls hard all the way to the redline. Truly a concourse-standard example.",
      "price": 49500.0,
